{
  "stem": "8352.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it's plugged.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] I-- we were still in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The factory that we were working at, that Braubach gasoline factory, it was bombarded twice during that period we were there, in that Rehmsdorf camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We happen to-- with the German instructors-- to rebuild it, keep it going again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One time, they made a mistake and they throw a bomb in the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And quite a few people got killed on the-- on that-- from that bomb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was always at nighttime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After they bombarded and destroyed a-- the factory, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] those SS were very angry and mad.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were kickin' us and beatin' us, and puttin' all the revenge out on us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they kept on tellin' us, we will kill you all out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No one of you will ever survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That, we had, every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --just lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't have anybody to talk to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody was wild.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody was trying to-- to be friendly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Everybody was trying just to take care about themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It took [SIGHS] quite a while, two times, to rebuild the factory and make it gone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was starting to get cold, gettin' toward the fall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They would not let us in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They kept us out-- outside on the-- on the-- on the yard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] And that was going on for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
